high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn left to look at the coffee table.
Get the watch on the left end of the coffee table.
Turn left, go forward, then turn left to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a watch in the light of the lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and then right to face the brown coffee table.
Pick up the watch from the left side of the coffee table.
Take the watch and turn around to the large window in the corner.
Hold the watch and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a watch and take it to turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and face the coffee table with the plate on it.
Pick up the watch that's next to the plate on the coffee table.
Turn around and walk to the lamp in the right corner of the room.
Use the watch to turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To turn on a lamp with a watch.
